      <title>能源部长表示欧盟今年必须减少俄罗斯液化天然气进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-16/war-in-ukraine-eu-aims-to-reduce-russian-lng-imports-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[能源专员卡德里·西姆森表示，欧盟正在“逐步”向俄罗斯液化天然气进口商施加更大压力，要求其减少今年的采购量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-16/war-in-ukraine-eu-aims-to-reduce-russian-lng-imports-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 09:04:20 GMT</pubDate>
